\begin_inset Formula $\mbox{Ad}_{g}X=gXg^{-1}$
\end_inset

 of 
\begin_inset Formula $g\in G$
\end_inset

 on 
\begin_inset Formula $X\in\mathfrak{g}$
\end_inset

